OL,3,EWIPEOUT 2097GSaturn````````````````````
OL,4,BBrrmm-brrm! Whoooosh! Wheeeeeeeeeee!   
OL,5,BThese are the sounds of Wipeout 2097.  
OL,7,FThis would be a good time to mention   
OL,8,Fthat the most famous aspect of Wipeout 
OL,9,F2097's PlayStation incarnation - the   
OL,10,Fsoundtrack - has been replaced here by 
OL,11,Fa version that does not feature Sony   
OL,12,Fmusical artistes.                      
OL,14,BWe could make a stupid joke about the  
OL,15,Bmusic being done by Bjorn Again, but we
OL,16,Bcan't really be bothered. But what     
OL,17,Babout the rest of the game? It's a     
OL,18,Bhardcore "dancefloor" space racing     
OL,19,Bgame - with weapons!                   
