OL,3,EWIPEOUT 2097GSaturn````````````````````
OL,5,BSaturn owners will be chuffed that,    
OL,6,Bsound aside, Wipeout 2097 has made the 
OL,7,Btransition from the PlayStation more or
OL,8,Bless intact. From the front-end to the 
OL,9,Bmiddle and back-ends, Wipeout 2097 is a
OL,10,Bspot-on conversion, lacking only some  
OL,11,Bof the fancier transparency effects.   
OL,13,FWhat this means is that Saturn owners  
OL,14,Fare now treated to one of the finest   
OL,15,Fracing games ever devised. On their    
OL,16,Fsystem probably only Sega Rally comes  
OL,17,Fclose in terms of gameplay and         
OL,18,Flastability value.                     
