OL,3,EWIPEOUT 2097GSaturn````````````````````
OL,5,BWipeout 2097 features garish, neon-lit,
OL,6,Broller-coaster tracks from around the  
OL,7,Bgalaxy, and a host of neat hovercraft  
OL,8,Bvehicles, which are power-uppable with 
OL,9,Ba number of superb weapons.            
OL,11,FOur favourite "bomb" sends a concrete  
OL,12,Fearthquake rippling along the track.   
OL,14,BThere will be few Saturn racing fans   
OL,15,Bwho'll be able to resist a conversion  
OL,16,Bof one of history's finest racing      
OL,17,Bgames, and they won't be disappointed. 
OL,18,BUnless their hands have melted, of     
OL,19,Bcourse!                                
